{"tid":1055090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「回帶」《東華》總善款數字＄121,888,888元","createTime":"2019-03-10T10:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T02:19:47.000Z","uid":26752,"like":10,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c591ab4b8556fa463e9e2d81ed7e11dbfcea1096","tid":1055090,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"2018年12月09日(日) 03:01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181209/photo/bkn-20181209030104973-1209_00862_001_01p.jpg?20181209033118\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181209%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181209030104973-1209_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20181209033118&h=d2b45743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫一年一度的大型籌款節目《歡樂滿東華》於凌晨時分圓滿結束，在一眾歌手及藝人努力下，經過一連串馬拉松式的節目，最後總善款數字為$121,888,888，成功打破往年紀錄。全晚籌得善款最高的表演環節是「東華友請小鳯姐」，由殿堂級歌手徐小鳯演唱歌曲《風雨同路》，共籌得善款數字為4,500,000港元！至於汪明荃「明荃之友會」的銀紙牌擺設連製作費13,800，義賣價128,000，最後籌得188,000。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181209/mobile/bkn-20181209030104973-1209_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181209%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181209030104973-1209_00862_001.html&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMN3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=6eb259e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181209/mobile/bkn-20181209030104973-1209_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2ef08ba55ad174fb30c6d57d43db88b9deb6a371","tid":1055090,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid